    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bs-links">
    <ul class="quick-links">
      <li><a href="./upgrading.html">{{_i}}从bootsrtap1.4版本升级{{/i}}</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/twitter/bootstrap/zipball/master">{{_i}}下载此文档{{/i}}</a></li>
